Type: Package
Package: ffscrapr
Title: ffscrapr - R Client for Fantasy Football League APIs
Version: 0.0.4.19
URL: https://ffscrapr.dynastyprocess.com, https://github.com/dynastyprocess/ffscrapr
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tan",
           family = "Ho",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tan@tanho.ca")
Description: This package abstracts the code required to
    call various Fantasy Football APIs (i.e. MFL, Sleeper, Fleaflicker,
    ESPN, Yahoo) and create methods that handle any authentication
    required, form appropriate calls, and return tidy & predictable
    dataframes which can be easily connected to other sources.
